{"tid":1759524,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣] [代用碳粉] 有無做開印刷嘅可以畀吓意見?","createTime":"2019-11-27T16:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T03:47:06.000Z","uid":167802,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6c0abd3a51db56db58b7cf2ca8d9198bb4e70519","tid":1759524,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:50:43.000Z","msg":"我有條文宣team<br />\n想問吓有無印刷大佬識得買平碳粉<br />\n我當然知道一分錢一分貨<br />\n但我真係唔希望因為貪平而敗咗部機&hellip;<br />\n所以想問吓用家意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟source緊CT202610/1/2/3系列<br />\n暫時搵倒有4間<br />\n- 365print<br />\n- OfficeMan<br />\n- FAX88<br />\n- Startprint<br />\n<br />\n但啲價錢真係差得遠得好緊要&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲printing quality有少少變差都唔緊要<br />\n反正文宣都唔係要特別靚<br />\n<br />\n最近抗爭到好窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a04867aa6d078a7d2300b49c692973a66fde19b","tid":1759524,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:51:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5a1f6164fdd05bc872dbe9baf1d3498546d5c37","tid":1759524,"uid":56231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T17:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n```"},{"pid":"e02447016f78c42849b3a81426a1bbba683cd92d","tid":1759524,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T17:03:43.000Z","msg":"我知道有出面有代印<br />\n但基於各樣考量暫時想用番自己機先"},{"pid":"432c4816a774af81557911875194c3966bdc4ed8","tid":1759524,"uid":104425,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e02447016f78c42849b3a81426a1bbba683cd92d","tid":1759524,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T17:03:43.000Z","msg":"我知道有出面有代印<br />\n但基於各樣考量暫時想用番自己機先"},"citedBy":2,"replyT